HB 511 Reengrossed 2026 Regular Session Glorioso
Abstract: Requires the Louisiana Commission on Law Enforcement and Administration
of Criminal Justice to establish the Law Enforcement Pursuit Safety and Technology
Grant Program.
Proposed law creates the Law Enforcement Pursuit Safety and Technology Grant Program
within the La. Commission on Law Enforcement and Administration of Criminal Justice
(commission) to fund state, parish, and municipal law enforcement agencies for the
acquisition and training related to technology and devices designed to safely terminate
high-speed vehicle pursuits.
